{"tid":928582,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"昨日情緒太激動","createTime":"2018-12-05T02:31:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-02T15:26:59.000Z","uid":182195,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"542334f1f7d6c899d8aa2a4430b6a2278c722076","tid":928582,"uid":182195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T02:31:39.000Z","msg":"昨日目擊另一半企圖跳樓<br />\n見佢衝出窗口驚到即時手震腳震<br />\n個時用埋飲奶嘅力去拉住佢<br />\n個腦空哂<br />\n剩係識一直喊 喊到氣喘咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n情緒太激動結果出現換氣症候群：<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/%E9%81%8E%E5%BA%A6%E6%8F%9B%E6%B0%A3%E7%97%87%E5%80%99%E7%BE%A4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%25E9%2581%258E%25E5%25BA%25A6%25E6%258F%259B%25E6%25B0%25A3%25E7%2597%2587%25E5%2580%2599%25E7%25BE%25A4&d=7rHVLdsKJorL0mK4yt4KGE%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=4870754d\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/%E9%81%8E%E5%BA%A6%E6%8F%9B%E6%B0%A3%E7%97%87%E5%80%99%E7%BE%A4</a><br />\n<br />\n係醫院check咗好耐先出到院<br />\n但係情緒仲好不穩<br />\n個腦會重覆閃過好多同一幕<br />\n搵咗大量朋友傾<br />\n好多都叫我take care自殺個位多點<br />\n叫我要理解佢<br />\n找輔導 講講下已讀不回<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n都係關心自殺果個多點<br />\n<br />\n情緒到呢刻完全冇抒解<br />\n長期同一個有自殺傾向嘅人相處個種壓力有人明白嗎？<br />\n個心keep住跳好快<br />\n手腳係咁震<br />\n應該點自救<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n連登有冇社工？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae9ffa18e1dd223ac7f6042f4a7a400d3ce969a5","tid":928582,"uid":207538,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"542334f1f7d6c899d8aa2a4430b6a2278c722076","tid":928582,"uid":182195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T02:31:39.000Z","msg":"昨日目擊另一半企圖跳樓<br />\n見佢衝出窗口